OL,3,CWill visitors to Cumbria be charged a
OL,4,C'tourist tax?'
OL,6,FNeither the Chancellor's speech
OL,7,Fyesterday nor the 150-page Budget
OL,8,Fdocument mentioned 'Cumbria' by name,
OL,9,Fas we've got used to across successive
OL,10,Fgovernments.
OL,12,FBut the announcement of a potential
OL,13,F'visitor levy' stands out as a policy
OL,14,Fthat could have a huge impact in the
OL,15,Fcounty.
OL,17,FIt's otherwise known as a 'tourist
OL,18,Ftax', like you pay on top of your
OL,19,Fhotel bill in many places overseas.
