OL,3,CWill visitors to Cumbria be charged a
OL,4,C'tourist tax?'
OL,6,FThe Scottish Government are already
OL,7,Fallowing councils north of the border
OL,8,Fto introduce such a charge, if they
OL,9,Fwant to.
OL,11,FDumfries and Galloway Council have
OL,12,Fjust finished a survey asking for
OL,13,Fviews on whether they should take up
OL,14,Fthe offer.
OL,16,FThe visitor economy is even more
OL,17,Fsignificant south of the border -
OL,18,FCumbria Tourism says the industry was
OL,19,Fworth #4.6bn locally last year,
OL,20,Fsupporting 74,000 jobs - 28% of the
OL,21,Fcounty's workforce.
