OL,3,CWill visitors to Cumbria be charged a
OL,4,C'tourist tax?'
OL,6,FJim Walker, president of Cumbria
OL,7,FTourism, told us: "our members really
OL,8,Fdon't want any extra charges, they're
OL,9,Falready in a difficult position
OL,10,Ffinancially."
OL,12,FBut, around England, it will be for
OL,13,Felected regional mayors to decide if
OL,14,Fthey want to add the levy on overnight
OL,15,Fstays, potentially raising money to
OL,16,Freinvest locally.
OL,18,FThe first mayoral election in Cumbria
OL,19,Fwill be in May 2027.
