OL,3,CWill visitors to Cumbria be charged a
OL,4,C'tourist tax?'
OL,6,FThere are two candidates declared so
OL,7,Ffar.
OL,9,FConservative Mike Starkie told us:
OL,10,F"Cumbria will not have a tourist tax
OL,11,Fif I am elected mayor."
OL,13,FHe said that's because it would
OL,14,F"further add to the financial
OL,15,Fpressures" on businesses and "would
OL,16,Fprove counterproductive for jobs and
OL,17,Fthe Cumbrian economy."
