OL,3,CWill visitors to Cumbria be charged a
OL,4,C'tourist tax?'
OL,6,FLiberal Democrat candidate Libby
OL,7,FBateman told us she hasn't finished
OL,8,Fresearching the policy yet, but: "I'm
OL,9,Fin favour of finding innovative ways
OL,10,Fto enable visitors to contribute to
OL,11,Fservices and infrastructure across
OL,12,FCumbria."
OL,14,FThe UK Government insist they will
OL,15,Fleave it to mayors to decide whether
OL,16,Fthey want to impose a "modest" charge
OL,17,F- with no specific figure proposed at
OL,18,Fthe moment.
