OL,3,CWill visitors to Cumbria be charged a
OL,4,C'tourist tax?'
OL,6,FBut the Budget document says that
OL,7,Fimplementing the policy would "fund
OL,8,Ffurther investment in growth locally,
OL,9,Fincluding the visitor economy."
OL,11,FA future Labour candidate for Mayor of
OL,12,FCumbria is likely to support the idea,
OL,13,Fand Reform UK, Green Party and other
OL,14,Fcandidates will also have to take
OL,15,Fpositions on this.
OL,17,FIt is likely to be a key issue of
OL,18,Fdebate heading into that election in
OL,19,F18 months time.
